{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21141.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"菲莉希亚","nameRight":"三栗菖蒲","textRight":"那么，@刚才的绘画比赛获胜的是谁？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"这次一定要决出胜负！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"谁的画更强！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"我还是觉得@全副武装的这幅画"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100501}],"textLeft":"比肌肉发达的画@更强大！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"嘁嘁嘁！这幅画上的佳子@长着刀枪不入的肌肉！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"什么啊！那是什么肌肉啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501}],"textLeft":"我说佳子，@你觉得哪一边更强？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":200}],"textRight":"是我画的肌肉佳子吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"是我画的武装佳子吧！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"夏目佳子","textLeft":"那、那个……@两位……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:301101:effect_emotion_sad_0][se:7224_fall_into]我想让你们比的是@『画功』啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"菲莉希亚","textRight":"？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"所以说……那个……@这场比赛并不是比"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"谁画的我比较强哦"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三栗菖蒲","textRight":"诶？那么结果呢？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"菲莉希亚","textRight":"你的意思是，@要比我们谁画得更像吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":200}],"textRight":"那你觉得，是哪边更像？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:301101:effect_emotion_sad_0][se:7224_fall_into]抱歉……@这次也是平手……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三栗菖蒲","textRight":"[chara:302801:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]诶诶~！？怎么回事！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"真的很抱歉……@可是，说实话……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"肌肉发达和@全副武装……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"两边都变形过头了……@从各种意义上来讲，@内容都太过丰富"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301101,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"我都分不清@哪一边更好了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"菲莉希亚","textRight":"又是平手啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"三栗菖蒲","textLeft":"可恶~接下来是什么比赛……@我好想赢啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"菲莉希亚","textRight":"既然搞得那么麻烦……@那就一定要赢……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"夏目佳子","textLeft":"（她们两个都……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"（忘记要打倒对方的事了……@太好啦）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"